Input 
a word

Process
1. Initializing the array
2. randomly choose a word
3. prompt the user to make a word using letters one letter at a time 
4. check if the user's guess is letter
5. keep track of the users guess
6. prompt the user how many guesses are left after each guess
7. when the user's guess exceeds five make them lose the game
8. check if the users guess is write or wrong 
9. if the user guess is right show all the words he/she guessed so far 
   and blank letters they have not guessed yet
   and let them know they won and end the game
